  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13097012/switzerland-walking-holiday.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="walking holidays" data-udi="umb://media/d0a05ee25118406cb2133a7f151ddd7d" /></p>
<p><img style="width: 0px; height: 0px; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13089361/climate-action-plan-hero-838x330.jpg?width=0&amp;height=0" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/2a04a7d8f96e4ed095539e0430ce5c35" /></p>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Explore Europe's lakes, mountains and coastlines on a walking holiday</h2>
<p>Whether you’re hiking to take photos of the spectacular scenery, trekking to uncover the local wildlife, wandering between restaurants to enjoy the local cuisine, or walking for the sheer joy of it, the Lakes, Mountains and coastlines of Europe are a walker’s paradise.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/2146c02aa3364cbeb1c0ef9561bc4426" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2146c02aa3364cbeb1c0ef9561bc4426}" title="Next Summer" class="c-btn">View Walking Holidays 2024</a></p>
<h3><strong>Included guided walks </strong></h3>
<p>We’re offering up to two guided walks per week in selected resorts. These are exclusive to Inghams, so join your fellow travellers and enjoy the incredible scenery, hidden trails and expert advice from a professional, local guide.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/419dea98f6194619b18de27172090063" href="/{localLink:umb://document/419dea98f6194619b18de27172090063}" title="Guided Walks" class="c-btn">Find out more</a></p>
<p> </p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Why book a walking holiday with Inghams?</h2>
<div class="g4">
<h3 class="white_box_shadow">Our walking holidays offer total flexibility</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13089978/walkers-mountains-alps-314x193.jpg" alt="Self Guided Walking Holidays" data-udi="umb://media/890f49005ee74077a788bfe55aaa96cd" /></p>
<p>On our walking holidays, you'll be free to explore on your own terms. Whether you want to take a leisurely stroll or try something more strenuous, you'll have the freedom to design your own walking adventure.</p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>Explore locally with ease from your doorstep</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13089977/hotel-gondola-314x193.jpg" alt="Local walks Alps Summer" data-udi="umb://media/c992a4e22aa64d13905081656c0a6366" /></p>
<p>Located in the heart of some of Europe's most stunning scenery, you'll stay in hotels that have everything you need on your doorstep so that you can get out and explore as soon as you wake up.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>See more, do more and discover more</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13089976/amalfi-coast-314x193.jpg" alt="Amalfi Coast" data-udi="umb://media/9ec30b529208452ab62dd884a16a0c63" /></p>
<p>When you travel with us you'll experience a lot more than you would on a typical walking holiday. We've chosen our European resorts for their culture and cuisine, as well as their endless activities and sights.</p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Walking Holiday Destinations</h2>
<p>We offer summer walking holidays across five European countries in some of the most iconic and beautiful destinations as well as lesser known resorts. </p>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/7f4620da7b6b476c96484e1d403801cc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7f4620da7b6b476c96484e1d403801cc}" title="Walking in Italy">Italy</a></h2>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/21c1e3e8d6be4c0fbbf64e72cf57a152" href="/{localLink:umb://document/21c1e3e8d6be4c0fbbf64e72cf57a152}" title="Walking Holidays in Italy"><img src="/media/13089972/italy-walking-hill-501x239.jpg" alt="Italy Walking Holiday" data-udi="umb://media/465c403a01db433eb47cd848e6437a46" /></a></p>
<p><span>From lake side promenades to wandering through the mountains, <a data-udi="umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904}" title="Italy">Italy</a> is full of variety.</span></p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/21c1e3e8d6be4c0fbbf64e72cf57a152" href="/{localLink:umb://document/21c1e3e8d6be4c0fbbf64e72cf57a152}" title="Walking Holidays in Italy" class="c-btn">View Italy holidays</a></div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/3d69090ac5714abb914063b47d753d06" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3d69090ac5714abb914063b47d753d06}" title="Walking in Austria">Austria</a></h2>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/021747e7ec9e48119452b165217e4380" href="/{localLink:umb://document/021747e7ec9e48119452b165217e4380}" title="Walking Holidays in Austria"><img src="/media/13089968/austria-walking-path-501x239.jpg" alt="Austria Walking Holiday" data-udi="umb://media/4ea7eb7e867a42e49e3b88aa0e5107d1" /></a></p>
<p><span><a data-udi="umb://document/c9325d9a77054a3c8190f3ab0da21760" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c9325d9a77054a3c8190f3ab0da21760}" title="Austria">Austria’s</a> beautiful mountain trails are brilliant for walkers with an interest in wildlife and nature.</span></p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/021747e7ec9e48119452b165217e4380" href="/{localLink:umb://document/021747e7ec9e48119452b165217e4380}" title="Walking Holidays in Austria" class="c-btn">View Austria holidays</a></div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/c92e399271ce40fdadbd79019fd5bf01" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c92e399271ce40fdadbd79019fd5bf01}" title="Walking in Switzerland">Switzerland</a></h2>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/26f1f8470b704d81a458b3fd804c271c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/26f1f8470b704d81a458b3fd804c271c}" title="Walking Holidays in Switzerland"><img src="/media/13090013/alpine-walking-summer-501-x239v2.jpg" alt="Switzerland summer walking" data-udi="umb://media/442b6cb22c3a443fa44de325d26859ed" /></a></p>
<p><span><a data-udi="umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d}" title="Switzerland">Switzerland</a> has some of the most dramatic mountain scenery in Europe – perfect for scenic strolls.</span></p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d}" title="Switzerland" class="c-btn">View Switzerland holidays</a></div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/07830ab1ba234ffd808ba9882fdd1f0f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/07830ab1ba234ffd808ba9882fdd1f0f}" title="Walking in Slovenia">Slovenia</a></h2>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/119b00d6f7e44bfc9192ccd47c0d7726" href="/{localLink:umb://document/119b00d6f7e44bfc9192ccd47c0d7726}" title="Walking Holidays in Slovenia"><img src="/media/13089934/zelenci-lake-kranjska-lake-501x239.jpg" alt="Slovenia Walking Holiday" data-udi="umb://media/9b0e7ba85ec54888bd00ae138dc28c66" /></a></p>
<p><span><a data-udi="umb://document/eb90f98d70e84089a8cb145d8e46e049" href="/{localLink:umb://document/eb90f98d70e84089a8cb145d8e46e049}" title="Slovenia">Slovenia</a> is a hidden gem, full of beautiful walks suitable for avid trekkers and gentle strollers.</span></p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/eb90f98d70e84089a8cb145d8e46e049" href="/{localLink:umb://document/eb90f98d70e84089a8cb145d8e46e049}" title="Slovenia" class="c-btn">View Slovenia holidays</a></div>
</div>
<div style="overflow-x: auto; float: center;"></div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/3af7f8dde05d46ecbb22bda488d94639" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3af7f8dde05d46ecbb22bda488d94639}" title="Walking in France">France</a></h2>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/93d2e05f5cc64bb9bc75dac532d8c42b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/93d2e05f5cc64bb9bc75dac532d8c42b}" title="Walking Holidays in France"><img src="/media/13089969/lake-annecy-boardwalk-501x239.jpg" alt="France Walking Holiday" data-udi="umb://media/4fa4637bcc004054ae7409c248a409c0" /></a></p>
<p>Relax and reconnect with nature on a walking holiday in <a data-udi="umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf}" title="France">France</a>.</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf}" title="France" class="c-btn">View France holidays</a></div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/b99bc93beefb425a905ffd631cf6d85b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b99bc93beefb425a905ffd631cf6d85b}" title="Madeira">Madeira</a></h2>
<p><img style="width: 238px; height: 127px;" src="/media/13098591/são-jorge_adobestock_591761991.jpg?width=238&amp;height=127&amp;mode=max" alt="Madeira walking holidays" data-udi="umb://media/9a3c0e3aeb1d4c9fab2c92de6610120c" /></p>
<p>Enjoy endless trails &amp; stunning ocean views on the beautiful island of Madeira. </p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/b99bc93beefb425a905ffd631cf6d85b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b99bc93beefb425a905ffd631cf6d85b}" title="Madeira" class="c-btn">View Madeira holidays</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/c9869bf0e4e9431d98d0277c1db49284" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c9869bf0e4e9431d98d0277c1db49284}" title="Deals" class="c-btn">View all deals</a></p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<div style="overflow-x: auto; float: center;"></div>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Discover more walking inspiration</h2>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>Insider’s Guide: Our 8 favourite walks</h3>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/1ecd5c85420d4565baba3b4bb1d4dd02" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1ecd5c85420d4565baba3b4bb1d4dd02}" title="9 exceptional Alpine walks"><img src="/media/13067788/inghams-lakes-and-mountains-walking-holidays-insiders-guides-top-walks.jpg" alt="Our favourite walks in the Lakes &amp; Mountains" data-udi="umb://media/3de8feba80784314909319b85f13cf65" /></a></p>
<p>Our list of the most exciting, beautiful, and iconic walks.</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/1ecd5c85420d4565baba3b4bb1d4dd02" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1ecd5c85420d4565baba3b4bb1d4dd02}" title="Our favourite alpine walks" class="c-btn">View our guide</a></div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>Insider's Guide: National Walking Month</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13067787/inghams-lakes-and-mountains-walking-holidays-france.jpg" alt="National Walking Month" data-udi="umb://media/6d904cddc2b1421faa097b0fa7903a08" /></p>
<p><span>Get the inside scoop on our experts favourite walks.</span></p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/7bc0a18c4c2742478fcc168b36655637" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7bc0a18c4c2742478fcc168b36655637}" title="Grab your boots for National Walking Month" class="c-btn">View our guide</a></div>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Walking Guidebooks</h2>
</div>
<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>Save 20% on Cicerone Walking Guidebooks</h2>
<p><img src="/media/13099474/inghams-image.png" alt="walking" data-udi="umb://media/4345b78fa56c4089a7025ad9d99b7a76" /></p>
<p>Cicerone publish over 350 different walking guidebooks including many which cover Inghams <a data-udi="umb://document/991245ba65ff4b36a0ec3d208715ed80" href="/{localLink:umb://document/991245ba65ff4b36a0ec3d208715ed80}" title="Destinations">Walking destinations</a>. We’re pleased to offer our guests an exclusive <a href="https://www.cicerone.co.uk/" title="Cicerone.co.uk">20% off all Cicerone titles</a>.</p>
<p>Book your summer holiday with Inghams, and we’ll send you a voucher code to claim your 20% discount.</p>
</div>
</div>
